      "description": "Tests for the **Catalog** microservice (`{{catalogUrl}}`, port 3000).\n\nReturns product metadata: `sku`, `title`, `price`, and `image`.\n\n| Request | Validates |\n| --- | --- |\n| `GET /catalog` | 200, array of ≥4 items; stores SKUs in `catalogSkus` |\n| `GET /catalog/:sku` (exists) | 200, returns Pen (`111111`) |\n| `GET /catalog/:sku` (404) | 404 for unknown SKU |"
